    <description>When a Gustie changes status this flow will update the user record with that new status and clear the Calendly link. Created in order to manage terminated employees.
1/13/20: Added email notification functionality.
2/5/21: Updated logic to avoid errors when user is not found.
7/30/21 Updated logic to update the HR Worker Team and Subteam whenever they change. Also added the functionality to remove the Distribution Engine License. Note: It happens 1-2 min after flow initiated.
1/31/22 Revised version to fix HR Worker Table bug that was incorrectly overwriting User field data. Updated to avoid Mixed DML error.</description>
